description: Demolition of existing buildings and structures in and around Olympus Square and the construction of 400 mixed tenure dwellings (use class C3), 232sqm (GIA) of mixed retail/ cafe floorspace (use class A1/A3); 453sqm (GIA) of community use (use class D1); a 62.4sqm (GIA) management office (Class B1); new pedestrian and vehicular access routes; car parking (Site: 60 replacement and 8 new disabled spaces / Wider Estate:174); landscape and public realm improvements; refurbishment works associated with the ground floor entrance lobby and podium of the existing Seaton Point tower and all associated infrastructure, including an energy centre.
